[Ender''s War](https://openlibrary.org/works/OL49619W)
See also:

 - [Ender''s Game: 1/2](https://openlibrary.org/works/OL19647657W/Ender''s_Game._1_2)

  [1]: http://www.hatrack.com/osc/books/endersgame/', 'In a future threatened by alien invasion, gifted child Ender Wiggin endures brutal military training through simulated battles, uncovering his genius amid isolation and ethical dilemmas.', 1985, '8420434191', '9781857237207', 330, NULL, 717, 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/8185357-L.jpg', '/works/OL49488W', NULL, '2005', 'English', NULL, 1, 0, 'enders-game-orson-scott-card', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 'public', '2026-03-16 21:30:33', '2026-03-22 20:32:05');
